<component name="NrrdReader" category="DataIO">
  <overview>
    <authors>
      <author>David Weinstein</author>
      <author>Martin Cole</author>
    </authors>
    <summary>Open a raw nrrd or a SCIRun wrapped nrrd.</summary>
    <description>

    <p>Interface to introdude a NrrdData into the net. NrrdReader can
    open a raw nrrd, or a previously saved SCIRun wrapped nrrd
    (NrrdData). If the first axis is vector or tensor data, make sure
    that the nrrdKind for that axis is set appropriately.  This can be
    checked via the <modref package="Teem" name="NrrdInfo"/> module
    and changed via the <modref package="Teem" name="UnuAxinfo"/>
    module.</p>

    </description>
    <examplesr>Teem/nets/test/io.net</examplesr>
  </overview>
  <io>
    <inputs lastportdynamic="no">
    </inputs>
    <outputs>
      <port>
        <name>Output Data</name>
	<datatype>SCIRun::Nrrd</datatype>
      </port>
    </outputs>
  </io>
  <testing>
  </testing>
</component>
